@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p class="mb-4">Last Updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM d, yyyy")</p>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Cobble! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform. Cobble is designed to help organizations manage member information securely in one centralized location.</p>
            <p>Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By accessing or using Cobble, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by all the terms outlined in this policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect several types of information from and about users of our platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: This includes email addresses, phone numbers, physical addresses, names, and other contact details provided during registration or profile updates.</li>
                <li><strong>Profile Information</strong>: Information you provide in your user profile, including profile pictures, emergency contacts, and other optional details.</li>
                <li><strong>Organization-Specific Information</strong>: Additional data required by your organization, which may include specialized information like medical details for sports clubs or assignment schedules for academic institutions.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Information about how you access and use the platform, including login times, features used, and interactions within the system.</li>
                <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: Data about the devices you use to access Cobble, including IP address, browser type, operating system, and device identifiers.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Creating and maintaining your account</li>
                <li>Providing the services requested by your organization</li>
                <li>Personalizing your experience on the platform</li>
                <li>Communicating with you about your account or the services</li>
                <li>Sending notifications based on your preferences</li>
                <li>Improving and optimizing our platform</li>
                <li>Ensuring the security and integrity of our services</li>
                <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>4. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We are committed to maintaining the confidentiality of your information. We share your data only in the following circumstances:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Within Your Organization</strong>: Information is shared with authorized members of your organization based on their permission levels and roles.</li>
                <li><strong>Service Providers</strong>: We may share data with trusted third-party service providers who help us operate our platform, such as hosting services, email delivery services, and analytics providers.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Requirements</strong>: We may disclose information if required by law, regulation, legal process, or governmental request.</li>
                <li><strong>Business Transfers</strong>: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, user information may be transferred as part of the transaction.</li>
                <li><strong>With Your Consent</strong>: We may share information with third parties when you provide explicit consent.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>5. Contact Information</h2>
            <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>
                Cobble Privacy Team<br />
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5" style="font-style: italic; color: var(--text-light); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-top: 1rem;">
            <p>© @DateTime.Now.Year Cobble. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>